snippet.textDisplay: Coke studio this season....rocks. I have been the avid follower of coke studio pak especially Charkaha Nolakha and the Led Zep bit. This season has me jumping over every single one. Started with Cerejo and now Amit. This is the perfect blend of advanced jazz and indian, All songs of Amit are great. I guess coke/MTV allows artists to go no-holds-barred :-) Sriram...my mom still unahappy about the "Ni" in Abogi :-)

snippet.textDisplay: My mother is a Carnatic music teacher. I showed her this song. She was upset with Shriram singing the "Ni" in the Agogi ragam. I had to make her understand that this is Fusion and is not to be viewed as pure Carnatic. All's fair here :-)
